name: Acid Rain
description:
Acid Rain is an interactive NFT.
Avoid the acid rain and try to survive as long as possible.
It's made for PC/Mac browsers, but also for Android/IOS.
Two different modes available:
2D: The rat only moves in the X axis (perfect for mobiles devices).
3D: The rat moves in the X and Y axis (computer oriented).

Art and code by n0t4numb3r
Music by E-Gerät (soundcloud egerat)
